name: I want to leave
description:
Releitura da obra de Banksy pintada nos muros da Palestina.
A releitura trata-se de um alien flutuando com o seus balões, o que retrata a fuga interna de cada ser para irem atrás de seus sonhos.
Pintura em aquarela sobre tela.

Re-reading of Banksy's work painted on the walls of Palestine.
The reinterpretation is about an alien floating with his balloons, which portrays the inner flight of each being to go after their dreams.
Watercolor painting on canvas.

2479x3504px
